Package com.stefanbrenner.droplet.model

This package contains the droplet model interfaces.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
IAction Base interface for all droplet actions.
IActionDevice Base interface for all action devices that can be used in droplet.
ICamera Interface for camera devices.
IDevice Base interface for all devices that can be used with droplet.
IDroplet Interface for the base droplet object that contains all devices.
IDropletContext Interface that encapsulates the droplet context and it's base objects.
IDurationAction Interface for all droplet actions with a duration.
IFlash Interface for flash devices.
INotificationSupport Interface for notification support.
IValve Interface for valve devices.
 

Package com.stefanbrenner.droplet.model Description

This package contains the droplet model interfaces.
